{
  "stem": "12494.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they succeeded in notifying-- some of the girls succeeded in notifying their parents in our-- in our compound that they were in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And against all recommendations that they be quiet, the parents decided to make an application to the camp commander to see their daughter.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were taken away, and they were interrogated as to how did they know that their daughters were in-- daughter, or daughters, I don't know anymore [INAUDIBLE]-- were in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they chose to lie and say that they saw this group of girls march by and recognized their daughter, which was a lie.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because the Germans knew that they never marched those girls by our camp, so they knew that there was an underground correspondence.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not-- we were not involved with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Bergen-Belsen was not too bad while we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, there were three stages in Bergen-Belsen, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two of them while we were there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the beginning, it was just simply not enough food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the treatment was-- well, it was not good, but it was not murderous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then came the second stage, when Josef Kramer, the commander of Auschwitz, was moved from Auschwitz to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He became our commander on October 1.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was not used to the kind of treatment that the Jews got in Bergen-Belsen, so rations were reduced, and things became much harsher.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it-- you know, it didn't last very long, because in December, we-- we lost a lot of weight during those two months.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wondered all the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
